commit.message:
ENH: Add Enforce from PDF2.0 in viewer_preferences (#2511)

Closes #2509

In order to use it:

```
# to set it:
writer.viewer_preferences.enforce += writer.viewer_preferences.PRINT_SCALING
# to clear it:
writer.viewer_preferences.enforce = None
```
